We have successfully deployed a Gonka node using docker-compose, following the documentation precisely.
All steps were executed correctly and without any errors. We also exposed three ports to the public (8000, 5000, 26657) and verified that they are reachable from outside.
All container logs look normal — no errors are present.
We also performed the basic checks as described in the documentation, and everything appears to be functioning properly. For example:
